pfs 0.0.6
---------
Released December 2025
* Create thumbnails by using the `mobi.phosh.Thumbnailer` service
* pfs-open: Add `org.freedesktop.FileManager1` interface
* Internal cleanups
* Issues fixed:
    * https://gitlab.gnome.org/World/Phosh/pfs/-/issues/16
    * https://gitlab.gnome.org/guidog/pfs/-/issues/6
* Contributors:
    * Arun Mani J
    * Guido Günther
* UI translations:
    * Guido Günther (de)

pfs 0.0.5
---------
September 2025
* Allow to save files by pressing `<enter>`
* Make settings schema optional
* Make cargo installable
* Move to gtk-rs 0.10
* Issues fixed
    * https://gitlab.gnome.org/World/Phosh/pfs/-/issues/15
* Contributors:
    * Arun Mani J
    * Guido Günther

